{"tid":1468680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇見今晚個金毛,絕對有合理理由相信鄉黑已派人扮手足搞事！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T19:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:49:17.000Z","uid":12768,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3aa9fbb6b38e26d81f96c964cdaf1fe4ebde7507","tid":1468680,"uid":12768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:55:56.000Z","msg":"做得示威者，尤其勇武派，最怕俾人認到。<br />\n某d外貌特徵，尤其明顯嘅髮型都會盡量去隱藏，有咁低調得咁低調。<br />\n今晚直播睇到個金毛MK, 一直扇風點火，個人又咁燥，我個人唔會相信佢係和理非。如果佢行得咁前去打鳩個公安，相信如果佢係同路人，會係偏向做前線勇武派。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但問題：<br />\n1）疑似打記者同埋救護，呢點犯左大家嘅共識。<br />\n<br />\n2）金色頭髮太明顯，頭套或者帽都冇戴，會唔會太引人注目？ 好多前線都將個頭剪得大眾d,起碼冇咁易認。而且呢個年代仲有邊d人染個mk 金？ 耳環又係一個明顯特徵，會唔會帶個咁嘅野去抗爭呀。單係呢2點，口罩都唔駛戴啦。<br />\n<br />\n3）無錯，佢真係可以除口罩，除口罩飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要時間好長同人吹水。唔怕機場無死角cctv喎。<br />\n<br />\n4）睇直播有一下見到有個男人背脊去到頸位置紋左典型鄉黑style嘅紋身（唔識形容，即係又龍又虎果類)，似係有同伴。間中聽到部份人同佢一唱一和。<br />\n<br />\n最後去攔車呢個行為，我唔評論佢鬼唔鬼，但係引致出防暴嘅誘因之一。攔車等於叫黑警支援，其實果陣個公安上左救護車，我相信大部份人都知去搶救護入面嘅人係會有負面影響。係咪值得？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然，鄉黑都可以有真同路人。 但希望呢排各位手足小心d。割唔割現場手足自己分析，黑警可以扮自己被去拉人，鄉黑都可搵d後生嘅做下扇風點火工作，或者直接出手。<br />\n<br />\n一直以來，我地都話永不割蓆，但千其唔好俾人利用呢一點去搞事。<br />\n<br />\n最後，如果因為我純粹單睇直播d表面野，而有對金毛或前線有誤解，請隨便屌。"},{"pid":"82f67ed61f63c8563271c70d8b45579561792879","tid":1468680,"uid":213379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:56:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">813 重點<br />\n<br />\n1）<br />\n中國公安派卧底到機場示威 <br />\n喬裝成記者及示威人士 直接破壞一國兩制<br />\n<br />\n2）<br />\n香港政府連同機管局及各航空公司串連 <br />\n企圖製造示威者癱瘓機場情況<br />\n<br />\n3）<br />\n香港警察主動衝擊機場內示威人士並對女示威非禮<br />\n在機場範圍用槍指向遊客及示威人士</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a163b36565353e6752fee2cfafd42ab86b855d80","tid":1468680,"uid":270778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:59:02.000Z","msg":"係咪講哩個？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FyF1POY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFyF1POY.png&h=68d55252&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64ad345f4c2111ca130dece7d6a9ffb8e8c2c46f","tid":1468680,"uid":12768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a163b36565353e6752fee2cfafd42ab86b855d80","tid":1468680,"uid":270778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:59:02.000Z","msg":"係咪講哩個？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FyF1POY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFyF1POY.png&h=68d55252&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:05:42.000Z","msg":"機場現場同我拉走個4眼金毛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463735</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n係。上面個post 有幾張佢除口罩嘅相.<br />\n<br />\n提提各位手足，頭髮特徵好易認，要抗爭剪個大眾頭先啦。"},{"pid":"1f58f300d37a040a9a58c7e727b7cbec16f3c93e","tid":1468680,"uid":12768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:29:36.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"99d6e4b3a5dd6ea6ca4a0d2fdd041471cc955243","tid":1468680,"uid":85708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T21:15:45.000Z","msg":"無人識佢??"},{"pid":"60e52e4c5f236ec2a2eb067a417a4e0eac90bde1","tid":1468680,"uid":12768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df6aefa577c708381191b361090484eca012e2a","tid":1468680,"uid":12768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4a61d1cbb97a6de752202dd4b9bb49b6478635","tid":1468680,"uid":5172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:26:01.000Z","msg":"有份帶頭塞departure"},{"pid":"6812e2e01ac02405a67ef3839f82063782fdb98e","tid":1468680,"uid":232817,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:27:03.000Z","msg":"咪撚再捉鬼，毫無意義，<br />\n你冇可能完全阻止對家放鬼，我地只要堅持不割對家就冇符，<br />\n人無恥則無敵"},{"pid":"82734dd469b015437b29161240543722f0ef0e65","tid":1468680,"uid":244058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:29:29.000Z","msg":"(轉載)<br />\n<br />\n機場示威攻略<br />\n呢個係一定可以消滅臥底嘅辦法<br />\n<br />\n但凡有人搞事，全部向後退，一齊搵手指指佢大叫［臥底警察］因為<br />\n<br />\n1. 向後退嘅人一定比搞事嘅人多，因為臥底再多都唔過我哋啲人<br />\n<br />\n2. 就算佢唔係臥底係勇武派，全部人都話佢係臥底警察，咁佢做嘢嘅時候都唔會影響到民意，到時政府賴我哋示威者我哋又可以賴返係警察做（真相無人知，亦都唔需要知，我哋來抗爭唔係來做偵探）<br />\n<br />\n同意嘅，麻煩傳出去<br />\n#同意所以share<br />\n#冷靜D理性D<br />\n#我哋輸唔起輿論<br />\n#直播媒體年代任何人犯錯都會有record<br />\n#不割𥱊也不中伏"},{"pid":"60fe5698f07702b3b8e26b75fa00d2adb354cf4b","tid":1468680,"uid":244058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:30:35.000Z","msg":"手指住大叫臥底警察應該幾有用"},{"pid":"dc067b8f50170cb9e08626ddb0eb91cceba0e0db","tid":1468680,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:44:27.000Z","msg":"佢後尾點解個頭爆晒缸？"},{"pid":"e8637d52f5fbf6620d5cc14243d41cbbce59b74a","tid":1468680,"uid":287028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:49:01.000Z","msg":"講冇用。要有人做野"},{"pid":"e46654bd0a00edebcccad8908b2c0d5b3592c9a5","tid":1468680,"uid":12768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:52:30.000Z","msg":"或者咁講，唔好帶住仇恨去抗爭，好易俾人煽動情緒做錯決定。"},{"pid":"6447d6f3fcd734c753ae6ff278af720d209e16b0","tid":1468680,"uid":256246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:54:54.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係講個金毛，根本成個前場俾佢做commander咁耐都無人拉走佢已經好有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2d2494b61ddda1274fb49ddfa8af90e4f8009c","tid":1468680,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:59:14.000Z","msg":"本身見到想入黎話可能位金毛係一個好衝動既巴打，但樓主又分析得幾有道理"},{"pid":"00b01faf36c93722dbdc0499ee18411441814e08","tid":1468680,"uid":44071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:27:30.000Z","msg":"完全同意<br />\n<br />\n勇武係槍林彈雨中對抗警暴嗰班<br />\n恰平民恰遊客打記者打救護嘅行為唔係勇武係懦弱<br />\n唔好整臭勇武個名<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個月前線嘅勇武派個個智勇而深沉<br />\n唔係發癲就當自己係勇武派<br />\n<br />\n做埋呢d係懦夫行為<br />\n唔係勇武派"},{"pid":"40743c5e52c1573eed272814d74e1ea9d71aacaa","tid":1468680,"uid":12768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00b01faf36c93722dbdc0499ee18411441814e08","tid":1468680,"uid":44071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:27:30.000Z","msg":"完全同意<br />\n<br />\n勇武係槍林彈雨中對抗警暴嗰班<br />\n恰平民恰遊客打記者打救護嘅行為唔係勇武係懦弱<br />\n唔好整臭勇武個名<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個月前線嘅勇武派個個智勇而深沉<br />\n唔係發癲就當自己係勇武派<br />\n<br />\n做埋呢d係懦夫行為<br />\n唔係勇武派"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"救女人果一幕就真勇武喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}